snippet.textDisplay: I'd love to see a Mother Trilogy for Switch. That way we could play all 3 games not only on the go, but also in the U.S. hence we never got both Mother 1 or 3 in the U.S. Also they should make HD graphics of them with new 3D cgi graphics and cartoony animations like they did with both the Crash Bandicoot and Spyro trilogy games (although the animations and graphics would be more similar to both Yo-Kai Watch and Pokemon because it's an rpg game). It would bring back so many peoples' memories of when they played it as kids (yes I know it's not as popular as Mario or Zelda, and 2/3 of the games didn't get released in the U.S. so it won't be nostalgic, but it'll still be a fun experience)!
